Class IOFuncs

java.lang.Object

ch.bailu.gtk.glib.IOFuncs
All Implemented Interfaces:
PointerInterface
public class IOFuncs extends Record
A table of functions used to handle different types of #GIOChannel
in a generic way.

https://docs.gtk.org/glib/struct.IOFuncs.html
